{"tid":1831252,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【演員工會獎】畢彼特肉緊捉實前妻珍妮花慰問 網民嗌復合","createTime":"2020-01-20T09:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T07:06:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ccad821fa226797bb8c94c22bc93dd1938b7afdd","tid":1831252,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"第26屆美國演員工會頒獎禮（Screen Actors Guild Awards, SAGA）於香港時間今早舉行，型男畢彼特（Brad Pitt）與前妻珍妮花雅麗絲頓（Jennifer Aniston）雙雙獲獎，畢彼特在後台還肉緊捉住珍妮花的手，向對方祝賀，是兩人離婚15年以來，首次公開合體，日前有報道傳兩人已經秘密復合。<br />\n畢彼特憑《從前，有個荷里活》（Once Upon a Time...in Hollywood）獲得最佳男配角，他在台上致辭時，在台下的珍妮花被影到感觸拍手，而畢彼特更開心地狂錫獎座。而打扮性感的珍妮花則憑劇集《晨早直播室》（The Morning Show）獲得劇情組視后，她發表得獎感言時，畢彼特亦在後台專注地看着電視畫面，看似十分緊張前妻的表現。其後，兩人在後台碰面互相慰問，網友紛紛留言表示感動和驚訝，更希望二人如傳聞般可以復合。此外，澳洲雜誌八卦雜誌《NEW WEEKLY》日前爆料，指畢彼特與珍妮花已在墨西哥秘密再次結婚，不過發言人已經否認。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200120/large/1579498780_56f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579498780_56f6.jpg&h=c9ababcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200120/large/1579498789_8c5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579498789_8c5c.jpg&h=8c8e213f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200120/UKEQWJAK3QXIIAFTD3V2P7CNVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200120%2FUKEQWJAK3QXIIAFTD3V2P7CNVI%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV93vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=22712c18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200120%2FUKEQWJAK3QXIIAFTD3V2P7CNVI%2F&h=ae0c898f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200120/UKEQWJAK3QXIIAFTD3V2P7CNVI/</a>"},{"pid":"cf7b37e75049